Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.70,0:00:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 我是蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和空的夢幻超絕技看過了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.30,0:00:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了那個舞臺賭上了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.80,0:00:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的命運和最好的搭檔的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能再站在卡萊多的舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我找到了新的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 跟著我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假了 而且是一周呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以做好多想做的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此機會可以去柯美利西亞盡情玩玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在圖書館細心策劃新作的構思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算每天特訓空中飛人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 陪我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這麼興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來演米娜瑪麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.80,0:02:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去真正的卡萊多之星……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 沒……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空換好衣服請到老闆的辦公室去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個驚人消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件反射吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也有休假計畫被打亂的例子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是先做好最壞的打算比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定連吃的都沒有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃……明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐邀請我去她的舞臺客串演出？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是蕾拉的推薦 不願意就推辭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北極也好南極也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪里我都會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空要去蕾拉小姐的舞臺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見到蕾拉小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到Broadway去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著前面的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是空啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特 茱莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在蕾拉小姐的跟班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空一點也沒變的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多舞臺的苗木野空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是導演的麥卡•伯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 明天開始的一周請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.80,0:06:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 她是這個舞臺的作者兼監督的卡茜•蒂姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 衣服不改不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉炒了前任出演者的魷魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒魷魚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也算是位專業的演員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可蕾拉好像就是不中意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公演期間都不和導演或監督商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常人會做那種事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不會那麼做的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和沒有熱情的人站在一個舞臺上罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個讓大小姐為難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾放寬一下她的日程不好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找不到代替人你打算怎麼處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難為你趕來了 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.50,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是卡萊多劇團的休假只有一周時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的事我們來解決 不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一幕需要你出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那是很重要的場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鏡頭是舞臺後半場的薩洛美的跳舞鏡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒與悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛與恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貫注了薩洛美的全部熱情的場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要雜技藝術的表演來襯托出舞臺的陰暗面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你提升舞臺的溫度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升舞臺的溫度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大致的順序能對上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取什麼演技全由你 也就是即興演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即興演出嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快彩排演習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫王梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為崇拜蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.70,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年以第一名的成績入了卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.60,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 在新作裏演出主角的新人演員是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 論實力還在空之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.00,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我代替空出演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ROLLING FLAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我被蕾拉小姐選中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從開始就這樣算計著來到紐約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DARING FLAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIRACLE GREAT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了梅 已經鬧夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.00,0:09:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉選上的是我 趕快從這個舞臺上下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.00,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被選中是因為蕾拉小姐不知道有我這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是超活躍新人登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空好像沒有勝算的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣 請2個人都出場如何 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.00,0:09:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正有此意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣開始排演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再增加一套衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 很急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……總覺得缺點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了那個明天再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼送你們去賓館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近準備好了賓館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非說跟空一個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 不要說任性的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.40,0:10:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一個房間我才不幹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不要和梅一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘰裏咕嚕吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那精力留到明天拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.40,0:11:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如取消了賓館 二人都住我房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是紐約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.80,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我去試泡咖啡你們隨便些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 這個時候要衝水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且豆粒要減少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前小姐你不太喝咖啡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說了 真是幫了我忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.40,0:11:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 能對小姐有幫助真是光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.10,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐在這裏開始了新生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻超絕技對蕾拉小姐來說已經是過去的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣 請2個人都出場如何 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是我一個人被期待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要總是猶猶豫豫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶猶豫豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩人出場的話 如果不好好配合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出醜的是蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟蕾拉小姐好久沒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得碰頭有很多話想說 都因為你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐不是你一個人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟蕾拉小姐說說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在舞臺合作是我夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.00,0:12:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是為了讓蕾拉小姐認可我比你要強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.30,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不會敗給像你這樣讓蕾拉小姐受傷的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說空讓我受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你要是不和空一起表演夢幻超絕技的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐應該不會受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們二人都坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷是因為我疏忽大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算弄傷了肩膀 我還是繼續表演夢幻超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責備空是沒有必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不能像那時那樣地表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而也虧了這傷勢才開闢了新的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要是沒有肩膀的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐現在一定在更大的舞臺上……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.10,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我選了那個舞臺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.60,0:13:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演了那個夢幻超絕技後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說再也不能回到卡萊多舞臺時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從電影 舞臺 電視上發來很多工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我完成了那個夢幻超絕技後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼話題都不感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個時候……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來客人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢何時恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到能料理普通生活的話應該是一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再稍為提早點就感謝上帝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做這個吧 不會讓你後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《salome in vegas》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很新鮮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人造謠說我落魄至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.80,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Broadway這樣的小舞臺也演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種話我完全不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那邊有讓我再次燃燒的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.40,0:14:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾想“這裏是我的新舞臺”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且卡茜是我的新搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐的新搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐我會努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你說我是你的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蕾拉小姐一起演出是我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今後的夢想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的……嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.80,0:15:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛才你說的夢想明天就會實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……駁倒空 不是 咦……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐你現在的夢想在這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得泡出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.20,0:16:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且卡茜是我的新搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在已經不再是蕾拉小姐的搭檔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 大家走的路不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.60,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過會從蕾拉小姐嘴裏這麼清楚地說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐的一句話使我的心變得如此不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.10,0:16:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我還是不能獨當一面 真是沒出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這種心情明天的舞臺沒法表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐所屬的獅子座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其影子裏悄悄的站著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經迷失方向的 空的射手座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.30,0:17:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不要多想 盡情地發揮演出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用小狗般的眼神看東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.90,0:17:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請以從我這奪得薩洛美角色般的氣魄來站上舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩洛美 請為我跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.60,0:17:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不想跳 海倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這國土上只有一件事令你不如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許只有我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩洛美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰 你的肌膚如同剛下的雪般雪白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的唇……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩洛美 不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.60,0:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰 約翰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“請以從我這奪得薩洛美角色般的氣魄來站上舞臺”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備上臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.80,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海倫 這就為了你跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要聽我的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位 讓我們來決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引所有觀眾的心 壓倒我也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了回應蕾拉小姐的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有超過蕾拉小姐的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被你認可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會敗給梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會敗給空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏不了蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.60,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你想要什麼吧 說吧 薩洛美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.00,0:19:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的東西只有一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐即使在這裏也放射著最耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.10,0:20:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全還達不到蕾拉小姐的水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有勝過蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們這一周的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你們才讓演出這麼完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.00,0:20:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你們才讓卡茜明白了燃燒舞臺溫度的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.60,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那個才把我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.10,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 為了讓他們看到和空一起演出的火熱舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在卡萊多劇團時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.70,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經感到從後面追趕上來的你很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.80,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的你卻已感覺不到那種迫力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的時候能救自己的只有自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標是哪里 想抓住什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的只有你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.80,0:21:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的答案都在你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的夢想在這個舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.60,0:21:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那天告訴你的也是我珍惜的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.70,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“成為我的夢想吧 空”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你可以成功的 真正的卡萊多之星”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.30,0:21:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要失去夢想 請繼續追尋下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.10,0:21:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的前面會展開真正的卡萊多之星的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.90,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 期待你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟卡萊多的眾位問候一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 請儘管放心交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.30,0:22:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能看見夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.30,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐的事 我承認是誤解了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.30,0:22:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是說放棄了跟你的勝負之戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.30,0:22:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案在我心裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.85,0:23:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告\N卡萊多之星 新生之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.20,0:23:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看見那麼悲傷的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.90,0:23:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.80,0:23:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是場傷害了孩子的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.80,0:23:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧的蹦床真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.50,0:23:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放棄了和媽媽一起登臺的夢想了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.50,0:24:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓瑪莉奧恢復笑容！笑容！笑容！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.70,0:24:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想 飛向空
